OL,3,CMarc Albrighton pays tribute to
OL,4,C'incredible' chairman as crash inquest
OL,5,Cconcludes
OL,7,FEx-Leicester City's Marc Albrighton
OL,8,Fhas told ITV News Central when his
OL,9,Fclub's chairman died in a helicopter
OL,10,Fcrash he and his fellow players were
OL,11,Fleft with just "a feeling of pain".
OL,13,FHis comments come as the inquest into
OL,14,Fthe helicopter crash that killed the
OL,15,FLeicester City owner, Vichai
OL,16,FSrivaddhanaprabha, and four others
OL,17,Fconcluded the crash was accidental.
