OL,3,CMarc Albrighton pays tribute to
OL,4,C'incredible' chairman as crash inquest
OL,5,Cconcludes
OL,7,FThe helicopter spun out of control and
OL,8,Fburst into flames when it crashed
OL,9,Fwhile leaving the stadium after a
OL,10,Fmatch on Saturday 27 October 2018.
OL,12,FAs well as Mr Srivaddhanaprabha, the
OL,13,Fhelicopter's pilot Eric Swaffer, his
OL,14,Fpartner Izabela Lechowicz and
OL,15,Fpassengers Nusara Suknamai and
OL,16,FKaveporn Punpare also died.
OL,18,FMr Srivaddhanaprabha, a Tiah
OL,19,Fbillionaire, bought Leicester City in
OL,20,FAugust 2010.
