OL,3,CMarc Albrighton pays tribute to
OL,4,C'incredible' chairman as crash inquest
OL,5,Cconcludes
OL,7,FUnder his ownership, the club won its
OL,8,Ffirst-ever top-flight league title
OL,9,Fdespite being given odds of 5000/1 at
OL,10,Fthe start of the season.
OL,12,FAlbrighton was a key part of that
OL,13,Ffamous Leicester team. He was one of
OL,14,Fthe players Mr Srivaddhanaprabha
OL,15,Fgifted a sports car to for winning the
OL,16,Ftitle and one of the players who went
OL,17,Fto his funeral in Thailand.
