OL,3,CMarc Albrighton pays tribute to
OL,4,C'incredible' chairman as crash inquest
OL,5,Cconcludes
OL,7,FHe spent 10 years at Leicester City
OL,8,FF.C. before retiring in 2024. While at
OL,9,Fthe club, he played almost 240 matches
OL,10,Fand won the FA Cup and the Premier
OL,11,FLeague title.
OL,13,FWhilst his memories of Mr
OL,14,FSrivaddhanaprabha are tied to
OL,15,Ffootball, he first and foremost
OL,16,Fremembered him as a special person.
OL,18,F"He was fantastic for the club of
OL,19,FLeicester City, the city of Leicester,
OL,20,Fjust everyone involved in football
OL,21,Freally.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
