OL,3,CMarc Albrighton pays tribute to
OL,4,C'incredible' chairman as crash inquest
OL,5,Cconcludes
OL,7,F"There weren't many owners that were
OL,8,Fso hands on and thought about the club
OL,9,Fand the city as much as Vichai did.
OL,11,F"So an incredible man, and when we
OL,12,Flost him, it was just a feeling of
OL,13,Fpain.
OL,15,F"You just didn't know really what to
OL,16,Fdo in them next few days."
OL,18,FAlbrighton wasn't surprised at the
OL,19,Foutpouring of grief after Vichai
OL,20,FSrivaddhanaprabha's death:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
