OL,3,CMarc Albrighton pays tribute to
OL,4,C'incredible' chairman as crash inquest
OL,5,Cconcludes
OL,7,F"We've seen the impact that he had
OL,8,Faround the city of Leicester, around
OL,9,Fthe football club, even in his
OL,10,Fhomeland as well.
OL,12,F"He was just a breath of fresh air for
OL,13,Ffootball. There's not many owners of
OL,14,Ftop premier league clubs that are the
OL,15,Fway that he is.
OL,17,F"So I think... it was a loss to
OL,18,Feveryone. It was a loss to football.
OL,19,FIt was a loss to life.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
