OL,3,CMarc Albrighton pays tribute to
OL,4,C'incredible' chairman as crash inquest
OL,5,Cconcludes
OL,7,F"It certainly didn't surprise me of
OL,8,Fhow much he had impacted so many
OL,9,Fpeople's lives.
OL,11,F"I fully expected the turn outs to all
OL,12,Fthe events and the flowers. I
OL,13,Fcertainly expected all that."
OL,15,F"He brought an air of stability. He
OL,16,Fbrought positivity. He had a vision
OL,17,Ffor the club and where he wanted it to
OL,18,Fbe.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
