OL,3,CMarc Albrighton pays tribute to
OL,4,C'incredible' chairman as crash inquest
OL,5,Cconcludes
OL,7,F"I think it got there a lot quicker
OL,8,Fthan even he expected but he did make
OL,9,Feveryone believe.
OL,11,F"I know a lot of people say that about
OL,12,Fcertain people when they passed but he
OL,13,Fsold you a dream but he didn't just
OL,14,Fsell it to you he was a part of making
OL,15,Fit happen.
OL,17,F"They called him the possible man
OL,18,F(because he made the impossible
OL,19,Fpossible).
